<h1 class="display-6">Monitoring</h1>
<p>
The purpose of the monitoring service is to collect and visualize metrics generated by the data processing components.
The monitoring service contains 2 components <a href="https://prometheus.io/">Prometheus</a> and <a href="https://grafana.com/">Grafana</a>.
<br>
<br>
Prometheus is a monitoring and alerting toolkit, often used as a backend database for Grafana.
Grafana is a complete observability stack that allows you to monitor and analyze metrics, logs and traces. It allows you to query, visualize, alert on and understand your data. 
</p>
<table class="table table-hover">
  <tr>
    <th>Service</th>
    <th>Host</th>
  </tr>
    {% for host in groups['monitor'] %}
    <tr>
      <td>Grafana</td>
      <td><a href="https://{{ host }}:{{ grafana_port }}" target="_blank">{{ host }}</a></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Prometheus</td>
      <td><a href="https://{{ host }}:{{ prometheus_port }}" target="_blank">{{ host }}</a></td>
    </tr>
    {% endfor %}
</table>
